  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2009-03-12",
    "date": "2009-03-25T17:46:40Z",
    "text": "Fairness in Cocaine Sentencing Act of 2009- Amends the Controlled Substances Act and the Controlled Substances Import and Export Act to eliminate: (1) increased and mandatory minimum penalties for drug offenses involving mixtures or substances which contain cocaine base (i.e., crack cocaine); and (2) restrictions on judicial authority to grant probation or suspended sentences for certain cocaine offenses."
  },
